sequenceDiagram
    participant Client as External Client
    participant Router as text-generation-router<br/>8033/TCP gRPC<br/>Optional TLS
    participant Queue as Validation + Queue<br/>(Internal)
    participant Batcher as Batcher<br/>(Weight-aware)
    participant Shard0 as text-generation-server<br/>Shard 0 (Python)<br/>UDS
    participant ShardN as text-generation-server<br/>Shard N (Python)<br/>UDS
    participant GPU as NVIDIA GPU<br/>CUDA 12.1

    Note over Client,GPU: Flow 1: Unary Text Generation Request

    Client->>Router: Generate RPC (gRPC/8033)<br/>Optional TLS/mTLS
    Router->>Queue: Validate request<br/>(temperature, top_k, top_p,<br/>sequence lengths, stop sequences)
    Queue->>Batcher: Enqueue validated request
    Batcher->>Batcher: Form optimal batch<br/>(prefill + next-token weights,<br/>padding thresholds)
    Batcher->>Shard0: Prefill RPC (UDS gRPC)<br/>/tmp/text-generation-server-0
    Shard0->>GPU: CUDA inference forward pass<br/>(Flash/Paged Attention)
    GPU-->>Shard0: Logits + KV cache
    loop Token Generation
        Batcher->>Shard0: NextToken RPC (UDS gRPC)
        Shard0->>GPU: Decode step
        GPU-->>Shard0: Next token logits
        Shard0-->>Batcher: Generated token
    end
    Batcher-->>Router: Complete generation result
    Router-->>Client: GenerationResponse (gRPC/8033)

    Note over Client,GPU: Flow 2: Multi-GPU Tensor Parallel Inference

    Note over Shard0,ShardN: Launcher spawns N shard processes (1 per GPU)
    Shard0->>ShardN: NCCL/GLOO init (29500/TCP)<br/>Intra-pod, plaintext
    Note over Shard0,ShardN: All shards load model weights<br/>(partitioned across GPUs)
    Batcher->>Shard0: Batch request via ServiceDiscovery
    Shard0->>ShardN: NCCL all-reduce<br/>(tensor parallel sync)
    ShardN-->>Shard0: Partial results merged
    Shard0-->>Batcher: Combined inference result

    Note over Client,GPU: Flow 3: Streaming Generation

    Client->>Router: GenerateStream RPC<br/>(gRPC server-stream/8033)
    Router->>Batcher: Enqueue stream request
    Batcher->>Shard0: Prefill RPC (UDS)
    Shard0->>GPU: Initial forward pass
    GPU-->>Shard0: First token
    loop Token-by-Token Streaming
        Shard0-->>Router: GenerationResponse (token)
        Router-->>Client: Streamed token (gRPC)
        Note over Router: Cancel check every token
        Batcher->>Shard0: NextToken RPC
        Shard0->>GPU: Decode step
        GPU-->>Shard0: Next token
    end
    Shard0-->>Router: Final token (stop condition)
    Router-->>Client: Stream complete
